name: Captain Panda - KuD-054
description: He used to be a common soldier in his regiment, until he is selected to be super soldier candidate. A few pandas lost in this experiment, but he completed all his experimental upgrade to be a super soldier. After he got his physical enhancement, he start to jump on wars for his nation as a captain of his regiment. Captain with super power bring victory to them and eventualy war ended and he dedicated rest of his life to help civilian from crime and such.
